divs: Sighting Detailsplain n simple i took 2 pics of myself with the sun behind me but both in a different position. after closely looking at them i see a black empty spot directly in front of the sun. im not sure if its just the exposure but am willing to send u the pics just incase. object was not vivible with the naked eye it was sunny and who i ask can look right into the sun and see? i think it was hiding there but hey maybe its nothing.
Summary: took 2 pics of myself and found a black disk hiding in the direct sunlight
